==English==

{{wikify}}


A [[juggling]] prop consisting of two hand sticks (dowels) and a third larger, hour-glass shaped stick.
The dowels or hand-sticks are about a foot long and usually wrapped with a high friction rubber tape.
The "Devil Stick" is about 20" long, about 1-1.5 inches in diameter at the ends and tappering down to about 1/2" at the center.
The "Devil Stick" is then manipulated using just the two hand-sticks.  Many manipulations are possible and quite pleasing to the eye.